Package: BayesSMCM
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Semiparametric Mixture Cure (Frailty) Model
Version: 0.1.0
Description: Bayesian Semiparametric Mixture Cure Model (SMCM) with both the inclusion and exclusion of a frailty component using MCMC algorithm and Stan.
